description: The hurricane has broken records for wind speed and number of days as a Category 5 storm.
title: Hurricane Irma Is One of the Strongest Storms In History
title_page: Hurricane Irma Is One of the Strongest Storms In History - The New York Times
text:
Here are all of the Atlantic hurricanes that reached Category 3 or stronger over the last 50 years. Hurricane Irma is highlighted in red .
No other hurricane has matched the strength of Irmaâ€™s winds so far east in the Atlantic.
